-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">In Mumbai, a short walk from Leopold Caf=
e and across the street from the Taj Hotel, where Puja&#8217;s parents were=
 married, a large stone arch-monument called Gateway of India sits between =
the city and the Arabian Sea. The British commissioned Gateway of India in =
1911 to commemorate the landing of King-Emperor George V and Queen-Empress =
Mary, the first British monarchs to visit India. After Indian Independence =
from Britain in 1947, the last British soldiers left India through the very=
 same gate.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Today, that structure is largely a tourist de=
stination. The real Gateway of India, as far as foreign companies and inves=
tors are concerned, is Reliance Industries.</p><h3 style=3D"color: #1a1a1a;=
 font-family: 'SF Compact Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Seg=
