/h3><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 1em 0;">Since I started writing Not Boring, one type of company has fa=
scinated me more than any other: the Asian tech conglomerate.</p><p style=
