p what type of business. Dhirubhai played this system masterfully to produc=
e Reliance&#8217;s early success, and from that strong position, Reliance w=
as well-prepared to take advantage of economic reforms. In 1991, under Prim=
e Minister P.V. Narasimha Rao and Finance Minister Manmohan Singh, India li=
